channel.title: Strange error with run and compiler, HELP PLEASE!
channel.description:
Hi! When I run my compiler or run, I just get this strange message:
Error occurred during initialization of VM java/lang/NoClassDefFoundError: java/lang/Object Tryck på en valfri tangent för att fortsätta...
What shall I do? Please help me.
P.S. Swedish computer, Tryck på en valfri tangent = Press any button to continue...[br][br][size=1]Posted on: January 09, 2008, 08:25:43 AM[/size][hr]Could anyone please help me? I realy want to start coding =(
